3) Document must have one main landmark: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/landmark-one-main?application=axeAPI a) ["#ext-element-1"] Fix all of the following: Document does not have a main landmark
4) Page must contain a level-one heading: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.5/page-has-heading-one?application=axeAPI a) ["#ext-element-1"] Fix all of the following: Page must have a level-one heading
